
Update_files.pl <hostName> 
  updates the relevant files (Files.lis) on hostName, 
  used for a single host or from DoAll.pl 

DoAll.pl 
  invokes Update_files.pl for all hosts in SardanaHosts.lis

Files.lis
  contains the files to be updated, used by Update_files.pls

Files.db
  contains info about the update state of each file, used by Updata_files.pl

SardanaHosts.lis 
  contains the host to be updated, used by DoAll.pl
 